text: A Man from Wyoming is a 1930 American World War I romance movie directed by Rowland V. Lee and starring Gary Cooper, June Collyer, Morgan Farley, Regis Toomey, Edgar Dearing, Emile Chautard. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1930 war movies Category:American war movies Category:1930s American romance movies Category:World War I movies Category:Paramount Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by Rowland V.
